name: Tune - Style
description:
Did you know that not all my LoRAs are hosted on CivitAI? Check out my Patreon to learn more!

What's this LoRA

This is a LoRA trained on commissioned pictures from a user on DeviantArt. It has a nice western cartoon style with a bias towards smaller body types.

My models are not trained to achieve the exact style of their source, but to change the general vibe of the image. They are also fine-tuned on anime models, so they may not work perfectly with realistic ones.

The images in the examples are created using only this LoRA and different models (mainly my custom):

  • https://civitai.com/models/24149

  • https://civitai.com/models/26332

  • https://civitai.com/models/28322

  • https://civitai.com/models/32022

  • https://civitai.com/models/33707

You don't need to specify a word to trigger this LoRA.

What's this trained on

This LoRA was trained on pictures commissioned by a user on DeviantArt. The pictures were generated using a mixture of my Mistoon_Ruby model and some of mine + 3rd party LoRAs.

Here's a sneak peek of the dataset for those of you who wants to get an idea of what to expect from the model:

Tips for this LoRA

  • For the pictures in the examples I've used a weight of 0.5, but even with a high value I've not seen much distortion

  • This LoRA works very well with my Sapphire and Anime models. I really like the aesthetic when used with the Sapphire model.

Guides

IF YOU ARE NEW TO STABLE DIFFUSION OR YOU HAVE PROBLEMS WITH MY MODELS, GO HERE: Guide

Learn how to create pictures like mine with my step-by-step tutorials:

  • Beginner's Guide

  • Prompting

  • My Workflow

  • Inpainting

  • ControlNet

If you want to create images with a high LoRA weight, I highly suggest you to check the tutorial.

Support My Work

If you want, you can support my work in different ways:

  • Check out my Patreon for exclusive content (early access to my models and exclusive polls): https://www.patreon.com/Inzaniak

  • Do you want a custom LoRA or picture? Check out my commission page: LoRA and Picture Commissions

  • If you want to support my work for free, you can also check out my music/art here:

    • Bandcamp

    • DeviantArt

A Special Thanks to my Patreon and Deviant Art Subscribers:

  • Tatsuya Murakami

  • malakaigodlike

  • Vascille Stuart

  • 3DCinetv

  • Stefan T
